headline: Republic Services, Inc. Sets Date for First Quarter 2025 Earnings Release and Conference Call
summary: Republic Services, Inc. (NYSE: RSG) will release its first quarter financial results after market close on Thursday, April 24, 2025, and host an investor conference call at 5 p.m. Eastern Time that day.
